<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./confirm_admin.css">
  <title>confirm_admin</title>

  <style>
    *{
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
body{

  background: #F4EDFA;
  margin: 0 auto;
  max-width: 800px;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}

.firstSection{

  background: #F4EDFA;
  box-shadow: 0px 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
}

section .imgUser{
background: linear-gradient(251.18deg, rgba(134, 90, 169, 0) 0%, rgba(134, 90, 169, 0.546875) 25.52%, rgba(134, 90, 169, 0.77385) 44.79%, #865AA9 67.19%);  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
  height: 280px;

}

.imgUser .imgInformations{
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: center;

  height: 100%;
  margin-left: 40px;
}

.imgInformations::before{
  content: '';
  width: 30px;
  height: 30px;
  background-color: #E05858;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.imgUser .imgInformations h2{

font-style: normal;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 48px;
line-height: 56px;
color: #EAEAEA;

}

.imgUser .imgInformations p {
  max-width: 373px;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 24px;
  color: #EFDBFE;
  margin-top: 24px;
}

.infoContainer{
  padding: 50px 40px;
}

.infoContainer h4{
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 24px;
  line-height: 29px;
  color: #62498A;
}

.infoContainer .container{
  margin-top:40px ;
}

.infoContainer .container >div{
  margin-top: 40px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.infoContainer .container >div strong{
  font-size: 24px;
  line-height: 29px;
  color: #575757;
}

.infoContainer .container >div strong + strong{
margin-top: 20px;
}

.infoContainer .container >div strong span{
  font-weight: 400;
}

.infoContainer .container h2{
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 32px;
  line-height: 40px;

  color: #62498A;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <section class="firstSection">
      <div class="imgUser">
        <div class="imgInformations">
            <div>
              <h2>Nova compra <br/> realizada</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="infoContainer">
        <h4>Um novo usuário realizou a compra de uma matrícula.</h4>

        <div class="container">
          <h2>Principais Dados</h2>

          <div>
            <strong>Nome: <span>{{courseUser.paidPersonalData.name}}</span></strong>
            <strong>CPF: <span>{{courseUser.paidPersonalData.cpf}}</span></strong>
            <strong>Telefone: <span>{{courseUser.paidPersonalData.cell_number}}</span></strong>
            <strong>Curso: <span>{{courseUser.paidPersonalData.course}}</span></strong>
            <strong>Valor da matrícula: <span>{{200}}</span></strong>
            <strong>Forma de Pagamento: <span>A definir</span></strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>


  </main>

</body>
</html>
